<cb:div>
<pb n="0070a" xml:id="I01.0028.0070a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0070a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 28</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0070a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>大覺寺元尼墓誌銘并序</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0070a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0070a0101">魏故車騎大將軍平舒文定邢公繼夫人大覺寺比丘元尼墓誌銘并序
<lb ed="I" n="0070a02" type="honorific"/>夫人諱純陀。法字智首。　恭宗景穆皇帝之孫。任城康王之第五女也。蟠根玉
<lb ed="I" n="0070a03" type="honorific"/>岫。擢質瓊林。姿色端華。風神桑婉。岐嶷發自齠年。窈窕傳於丱日。康王偏加深
<lb ed="I" n="0070a04" type="honorific"/>愛。見異眾女。長居懷抱之中。不<note n="0070001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩀌＝離【史】</note><app n="0070001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩀌</rdg></app>股掌之上。始及七歲。康王薨俎。天情孝性。不
<lb ed="I" n="0070a05" type="honorific"/>習而知。泣血茹憂。無捨晝夜。初笄之年。言歸穆氏。懃事女功。備宣婦德。良人既
<lb ed="I" n="0070a06" type="honorific"/>逝。半<note n="0070002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">軆＝體【史】</note><app n="0070002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">軆</rdg></app>云傾。慨絕三從。將循一醮。思姜水之<note n="0070003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30313"/>＝節【史】</note><app n="0070003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">節</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30313"/></rdg></app>。起黃鵠之歌。兄太傅文宣王。違
<lb ed="I" n="0070a07" type="honorific"/>義奪情。確焉不許。文定公高門盛德。才兼將相。運屬　文皇。契同魚水。名<note n="0070004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠖌＝冠【史】</note><app n="0070004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠖌</rdg></app>遂
<lb ed="I" n="0070a08" type="honorific"/>古。勳烈當時。婉然作配。來嬪君子。好如琴瑟。和若塤<note n="0070005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30528"/>＝箎【史】</note><app n="0070005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">箎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30528"/></rdg></app>。不言容宿。自同賓敬。奉
<lb ed="I" n="0070a09" type="honorific"/>姑盡<note n="0070006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">礼＝禮【史】</note><app n="0070006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">礼</rdg></app>。剋匪懈於一人。<note n="0070007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠁅＝處【史】</note><app n="0070007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠁅</rdg></app>姒唯雍。能燮諧於眾列。子散騎常侍遜。爰以咳襁。聖
<lb ed="I" n="0070a10" type="honorific"/>善遽捐。恩鞠備加。慈訓兼厚。大義深仁。隆於已出。故以教侔在織。言若斷機。用
<lb ed="I" n="0070a11" type="honorific"/>令此子成名剋<note n="0070008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB05655"/>＝搆【史】</note><app n="0070008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">搆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB05655"/></rdg></app>。兼機情獨悟。巧思絕倫。詩書礼辟。經目悉覽。紘綖組<note n="0070009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">絍＝紝【史】</note><app n="0070009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">紝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">絍</rdg></app>。入手
<lb ed="I" n="0070a12" type="honorific"/>能工。稀言慎語。白珪無玷。敬信然諾。黃金非重。巾帨公宮。不登袨異之服。箕<note n="0070010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">菷＝帚【史】</note><app n="0070010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">帚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">菷</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0070a13" type="honorific"/>貴室。必御浣濯之衣。信可以女宗一時。母儀千載。豈直聞言識行。觀色知情。及
<lb ed="I" n="0070a14" type="honorific"/>車騎謝世。思成夫德。夜不洵涕。朝<note n="0070011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30530"/>＝哭【史】</note><app n="0070011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">哭</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30530"/></rdg></app>銜悲。乃歎曰吾一生契闊。再<app type="star" corresp="#0070001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩀌</rdg></app>辛苦。既<note n="0070012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30534"/>＝慚【史】</note><app n="0070012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慚</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30534"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0070a15" type="honorific"/>靡他之<note n="0070013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">撡＝操【史】</note><app n="0070013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">操</lem><rdg wit="【原】">撡</rdg></app>。又愧不轉之心。爽德事人。不興他族。樂從苦生。果由因起。便捨身俗
<lb ed="I" n="0070a16" type="honorific"/>累。託<app type="star" corresp="#0070002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">軆</rdg></app>法門。棄<note n="0070014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30531"/>＝置【史】</note><app n="0070014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">置</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30531"/></rdg></app>愛津。栖遲正水。<note n="0070015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">愽＝博【史】</note><app n="0070015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">博</lem><rdg wit="【原】">愽</rdg></app>搜經藏。廣通<note n="0070016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢦶＝戒【史】</note><app n="0070016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢦶</rdg></app>律。珍寶六度。草芥千金。十
<lb ed="I" n="0070a17" type="honorific"/>善之報方臻。雙林之影遄滅。西河王魏慶。穆氏之出。即夫人外孫。宗室才英。聲
<lb ed="I" n="0070a18" type="honorific"/>芳藉甚。作守近畿。　帝城蒙潤。夫人往彼。<note n="0070017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB17554"/>＝遘【史】</note><app n="0070017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB17554"/></rdg></app>疾彌<note n="0070018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤱊＝留【史】</note><app n="0070018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">留</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤱊</rdg></app>。以冬十月己酉朔十三日
<lb ed="I" n="0070a19" type="honorific"/>辛酉。薨於熒陽郡解別館。子孫號慕。緇素興嗟。臨終醒寤。分明遺託。令別<note n="0070019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">塟＝葬【史】</note><app n="0070019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">葬</lem><rdg wit="【原】">塟</rdg></app>他
<lb ed="I" n="0070a20" type="honorific"/>所。以遂脩道之心。兒女式遵。不敢違　旨。粵以十一月戊寅朔七日甲申。卜窆
<lb ed="I" n="0070a21" type="honorific"/>於洛陽城西北一十五里。芒山西南。別名馬<note n="0070020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">鞌＝鞍【史】</note><app n="0070020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鞍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">鞌</rdg></app>小山之朝陽。金玉一毀。灰塵行
<lb ed="I" n="0070a22" type="honorific"/>及。謹勒石於泉廬。庶芳菲之相襲。其辭曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0070a23" type="honorific"/>金行不競。水運唯昌。於鑠二祖。龍飛鳳翔。繼文下武。疊聖重光。英明踵德。周封
<lb ed="I" n="0070a24" type="honorific"/>漢蒼。篤生<note n="0070021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30533"/>＝柔【史】</note><app n="0070021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">柔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30533"/></rdg></app>順。剋誕溫良。行齊槁木。貴等河魴。蓮開淥渚。日照層梁。谷蕈葛虆
<lb ed="I" n="0070a25" type="honorific"/>灌集鸝黃。言歸備禮。環珮鏗鏘。明同折軸。智若埋羊。惇和九族。雍睦分房。時順
<lb ed="I" n="0070a26" type="honorific"/>有極。榮落無常。昔為國小。今稱未亡。傾天已及。如何弗傷。<app type="star" corresp="#0070001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩀌</rdg></app>茲塵境。適彼玄場。
<lb ed="I" n="0070a27" type="honorific"/>幽監寂寂。天道芒芒。生浮命促。晝<note n="0070022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢭃＝短【史】</note><app n="0070022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">短</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢭃</rdg></app>宵長。一歸細柳。不反扶<note n="0070023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">桒＝桑【史】</note><app n="0070023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">桑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">桒</rdg></app>。霜凝青檟。風悲
<lb ed="I" n="0070a28" type="honorific"/>白楊。蕙臥蘭畹。無絕芬芳。
<lb ed="I" n="0070a29" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　維永安二年歲次己酉十一月戊寅朔七日甲申造</p>
